number of people's needs.

01:28:08.270 --> 01:28:14.060
So, a lot of how we think about
space at least is with SpaceX

01:28:14.060 --> 01:28:17.650
and other companies coming
on the fray is in terms

01:28:17.650 --> 01:28:18.950
of commercial interest, right?

01:28:18.950 --> 01:28:22.080
So the moon is open for business
and the things that Elon Musk is

01:28:22.080 --> 01:28:26.870
up to, for instance,
