01:29:15.580 --> 01:29:19.050
the narratives coming out of new
space companies that say, "Oh,

01:29:19.050 --> 01:29:21.600
we're going to make it
accessible by making it cheaper

01:29:21.600 --> 01:29:25.420
and it'll only be
$200,000", and, you know,

01:29:25.420 --> 01:29:27.950
not everybody will want
to sell their house

01:29:27.950 --> 01:29:32.300
