01:36:24.620 --> 01:36:27.080
with the concept of
environmental personhood

01:36:27.080 --> 01:36:29.880
and how we think
about environments

01:36:29.880 --> 01:36:32.090
and whether they have
life in them or not

01:36:32.090 --> 01:36:35.320
as being something
that belongs to us.

01:36:35.320 --> 01:36:38.850
So I hope you'll stick around.

01:36:38.850 --> 01:36:40.150
