understanding of ourselves.

03:01:17.560 --> 03:01:20.620
And I think if someone will
speaks to the commonality

03:01:20.620 --> 03:01:22.240
of experience, what
I mean it's very hard

03:01:22.240 --> 03:01:25.900
to imagine we're very different
when you see earth as, you know,

03:01:25.900 --> 03:01:29.250
a pixel on a, you
know, an image.

03:01:29.250 --> 03:01:31.310
