I think a lot more--

03:01:31.310 --> 03:01:33.680
a lot more alone but
also lot more connected,

03:01:33.680 --> 03:01:36.710
so I hope that that's
kind of the version

03:01:36.710 --> 03:01:39.010
of exploration that
we take forward.

