03:09:08.020 --> 03:09:11.540
But if we start thinking and I
think the next panel will talk

03:09:11.540 --> 03:09:12.840
about this a lot too, right?

03:09:12.840 --> 03:09:17.030
If we start imagining different
ways of relating to each other,

03:09:17.030 --> 03:09:18.640
resonating and also knowing

03:09:18.640 --> 03:09:21.940
that consensus is not
necessarily possible

03:09:21.940 --> 03:09:24.360
and that we don't want to all
